{"tid":1068812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭人　跳毛利戰舞　向基督城　穆斯林死者　致哀","createTime":"2019-03-19T13:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T13:23:14.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00e770e681b0d5c96991834e5d0572fdd65ee9ab","tid":1068812,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:18:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=blYY3H17Tlg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DblYY3H17Tlg&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=e4dc9254\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=blYY3H17Tlg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/26175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F26175&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=c10f4e52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/26175</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lt6GRghrmaU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dlt6GRghrmaU&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=4af75327\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lt6GRghrmaU</a><br />\n<br />\n一位老師要退休離開學校了，而這次北帕莫斯頓男子高中（Palmerston North Boys' High School）學生歡送他的方式，是一起跳毛利戰舞（HAKA）！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F40154&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=ef3dfd4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40154</a><br />\n<br />\n最近紐西蘭網友瘋傳一支令人心碎的影片。影片中，一位17歲男孩的葬禮上，朋友們跳起毛利戰舞「哈卡」（HAKA）為他送別。領舞男孩情緒幾近潰堤，但他哽咽強忍淚水、堅持跳完這支舞，送朋友最後一程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3732/3732864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3732%2F3732864.jpg&h=320e3598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／Anthony Hall）<br />\n<br />\n17歲的Jarom Rihari自殺身亡，朋友們感到錯愕、不捨。當他的靈車開離教堂時，一群青少年克制悲痛的情緒，列陣跳起「哈卡舞」，大聲呼喊、頓足、槌胸，氣勢磅礡而悲壯，這是他們對朋友最後、最高的敬意。<br />\n<br />\n「哈卡舞」是紐西蘭原住民毛利人的傳統舞蹈，在婚喪喜慶特殊場合經常出現，許多運動員甚至會在比賽前跳上一段「哈卡」，展現輸人不輸陣的氣勢。哈卡包含許多意思，像是戰爭中的勇猛士氣，還有對客人的歡迎，以及在各種場合舉辦的相聚儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=blYY3H17Tlg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DblYY3H17Tlg&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=e4dc9254\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=blYY3H17Tlg</a>"},{"pid":"27a70850fe047d3dedfe63468b99258abeca326e","tid":1068812,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9NiNfjd67JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9NiNfjd67JU&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=89ac28bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9NiNfjd67JU</a>"},{"pid":"3c81c929a92c2fb8d94ca50299a2bb8d6d0bc61f","tid":1068812,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"我地大學生都識dem beat"}]}